<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Encuesta Guardada</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #6366f1;
            --primary-dark: #4f46e5;
            --success: #10b981;
            --success-dark: #059669;
            --success-light: #d1fae5;
            --bg-light: #f9fafb;
            --text-dark: #1f2937;
            --text-medium: #4b5563;
            --text-light: #f3f4f6;
        }
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }
        
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-light), #e0e7ff);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .success-container {
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 8px 10px -6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
            transform: translateY(0);
            animation: slideIn 0.6s ease-out;
        }
        
        @keyframes slideIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
        
        .success-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--success), var(--success-dark));
            padding: 2rem;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .success-header::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            width: 150%;
            height: 150%;
            top: -80%;
            left: -25%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
            transform: rotate(-15deg);
        }
        
        .success-icon {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 0 auto;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--success);
            position: relative;
            animation: bounceIn 0.8s ease-out;
        }
        
        @keyframes bounceIn {
            0% {
                transform: scale(0);
            }
            50% {
                transform: scale(1.1);
            }
            70% {
                transform: scale(0.9);
            }
            100% {
                transform: scale(1);
            }
        }
        
        .success-icon::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 3px solid white;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: ripple 1.5s ease-out infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes ripple {
            0% {
                transform: scale(1);
                opacity: 0.4;
            }
            100% {
                transform: scale(1.5);
                opacity: 0;
            }
        }
        
        .success-body {
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .success-title {
            color: var(--success);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out;
        }
        
        .success-message {
            color: var(--text-medium);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            animation: fadeIn 1.2s ease-out;
        }
        
        .success-actions {
            animation: fadeIn 1.4s ease-out;
        }
        
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        .btn-primary {
            background-color: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.4);
        }
        
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: var(--primary-dark);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px -3px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.5);
        }
        
        .btn-icon {
            margin-right: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .confetti {
            position: absolute;
            width: 10px;
            height: 10px;
            background-color: #f59e0b;
            top: -10px;
            opacity: 0;
        }
        
        .confetti:nth-child(1) {
            left: 10%;
            transform: rotate(45deg);
            background-color: #ec4899;
            animation: fallConfetti 3s ease-out infinite;
            animation-delay: 0.1s;
        }
        
        .confetti:nth-child(2) {
            left: 20%;
            transform: rotate(15deg);
            background-color: #f59e0b;
            animation: fallConfetti 2.5s ease-out infinite;
            animation-delay: 0.3s;
        }
        
        .confetti:nth-child(3) {
            left: 30%;
            transform: rotate(35deg);
            background-color: #10b981;
            animation: fallConfetti 3.2s ease-out infinite;
            animation-delay: 0.5s;
        }
        
        .confetti:nth-child(4) {
            left: 40%;
            transform: rotate(65deg);
            background-color: #3b82f6;
            animation: fallConfetti 2.8s ease-out infinite;
            animation-delay: 0.2s;
        }
        
        .confetti:nth-child(5) {
            left: 50%;
            transform: rotate(25deg);
            background-color: #a855f7;
            animation: fallConfetti 3.5s ease-out infinite;
            animation-delay: 0.7s;
        }
        
        .confetti:nth-child(6) {
            left: 60%;
            transform: rotate(55deg);
            background-color: #f43f5e;
            animation: fallConfetti 3s ease-out infinite;
            animation-delay: 0.4s;
        }
        
        .confetti:nth-child(7) {
            left: 70%;
            transform: rotate(40deg);
            background-color: #eab308;
            animation: fallConfetti 2.7s ease-out infinite;
            animation-delay: 0.6s;
        }
        
        .confetti:nth-child(8) {
            left: 80%;
            transform: rotate(70deg);
            background-color: #06b6d4;
            animation: fallConfetti 3.3s ease-out infinite;
            animation-delay: 0.9s;
        }
        
        .confetti:nth-child(9) {
            left: 90%;
            transform: rotate(30deg);
            background-color: #8b5cf6;
            animation: fallConfetti 3.1s ease-out infinite;
            animation-delay: 0.8s;
        }
        
        @keyframes fallConfetti {
            0% {
                opacity: 1;
                top: -10px;
                transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg) scale(0.7);
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 0;
                top: 400px;
                transform: translateY(0) rotate(360deg) scale(0);
            }
        }
        
        .success-footer {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            padding: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 500px) {
            .success-container {
                border-radius: 12px;
            }
            
            .success-header {
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }
            
            .success-icon {
                width: 70px;
                height: 70px;
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .success-title {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }
            
            .success-message {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="success-container">
        <!-- Confetti elements -->
        <div class="confetti"></div>
        <div class="confetti"></div>
        <div class="confetti"></div>
        <div class="confetti"></div>
        <div class="confetti"></div>
        <div class="confetti"></div>
        <div class="confetti"></div>
        <div class="confetti"></div>
        <div class="confetti"></div>
        
        <div class="success-header">
            <div class="success-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-check"></i>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="success-body">
            <h2 class="success-title">¡Encuesta guardada con éxito!</h2>
            <p class="success-message">Tu encuesta ha sido registrada correctamente en nuestro sistema y ya está disponible para ser compartida.</p>
            
            <div class="success-actions">
                <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">
                    <i class="fas fa-home btn-icon"></i>
                    Volver al inicio
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="success-footer">
            Sistema de Encuestas &copy; 2025
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>